---
title: Cheesy Chipotle Breakfast Tacos Serves 2 | with Cabbage Slaw and Crispy Bacon
description: Breakfast tacos are always a good idea, especially when they come with a spicy kick! This savoury recipe includes fluffy scrambled eggs, crunchy cabbage slaw and crispy bacon for an all-round brunch favourite.
